== Requirements

* JRuby 1.1.1+
* Rails 2.0.2 (newer version may not work!)
* RubyGettext (for Windows: install poedit and add its bin directory to system path)

== Installation

* Modify config/initializers/config.rb, config/database.yml
* Prepare DB
rake db:migrate
rake db:init
* Translate pofiles to mofiles
rake gettext:makemo

== Running

* Start the fifo manager first
ruby script/fifo_manager

* Then start the web server(s)
ruby script/server
